{"tid":1176236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國攝影師鍾愛繁體字　拍下香港「城市詩意」","createTime":"2019-05-29T05:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T05:56:55.000Z","uid":1886,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3749d7d35b92a96e124188e9f17dbe2d5b616bd7","tid":1176236,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:31:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/art/多圖-法國攝影師鍾愛繁體字-拍下香港-城市詩意/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB%E9%8D%BE%E6%84%9B%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94%E5%AD%97-%E6%8B%8D%E4%B8%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A9%A9%E6%84%8F%2F&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LoMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=8822807d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB%E9%8D%BE%E6%84%9B%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94%E5%AD%97-%E6%8B%8D%E4%B8%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A9%A9%E6%84%8F%2F&h=131ae30f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/art/多圖-法國攝影師鍾愛繁體字-拍下香港-城市詩意/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港的獨特城市景觀往往成為藝術家的創作靈感，如密集式樓宇就曾成為已故知名攝影師 Michael Wolf 的重要素材。而法國攝影師 Romain Jacquet-Lagr&egrave;ze 則被香港街道招牌獨特的繁體中文字體所吸引，並拍攝成系列作品「城市詩意」。 <br />\n<br />\n穿梭於香港大街小巷，Jacquet-Lagr&egrave;ze 喜歡仔細欣賞形形色色的店舖招牌以及大廈名稱上的繁體字體。他指出，這些字體各具特色，並配合各種不同的設計風格，例如木刻或石刻、手工吹製的霓虹燈管、拼貼紙皮石、手繪等，是名副其實的藝術品。此外，他認為繁體字從古代流傳至今，是香港這樣一個高度現代化的城市中十分珍貴的歷史元素。<br />\n<br />\nJacquet-Lagr&egrave;ze 強調，真正讓每個招牌變得獨一無二的，是那「時間流逝的見證」。無論是招牌上剝落的油漆、失落的瓷磚，抑或破碎的霓虹燈，這些歲月侵蝕的痕跡賦予字體另一層意義，「成為時間的詩歌」。於是，這些年他拍下許多招牌上的文字，有的依舊鮮豔奪目，有的已經褪色。拍完回家後，他會請港人太太幫忙檢查記錄下的字體，並解釋其意思，同時藉此學習廣東話。<br />\n<br />\n儲下大量字體招牌後，Jacquet-Lagr&egrave;ze 將它們拼湊成不同字詞，像是「香港文化」、「新興文化」、「愛家」等，融合視覺與語言。"},{"pid":"b766dd0357c2a3baa653f6d171deadd1215983df","tid":1176236,"uid":1886,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"Romain Jacquet-Lagr&egrave;ze 來自法國，於巴黎東大學多媒體藝術學系碩士畢業，原為平面設計師。2011 年移居香港後，環境的衝擊令他更熱衷於攝影。高聳入雲的摩天大樓，便曾使 Jacquet-Lagr&egrave;ze 嘆為觀止，讓他更想要透過攝影表達他對這座城市的震撼感受。而香港最令他著迷的地方是，在幾何圖形般的市區環境中，香港人依舊過著多彩的生活。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Kowloon2BNight2B-2BE4B99DE9BE8D_kO900_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FKowloon2BNight2B-2BE4B99DE9BE8D_kO900_1200x0.jpg&h=4b29dde0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E5BF83E5BF83_A1yL5_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE5BF83E5BF83_A1yL5_1200x0.jpg&h=4ae178ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/45_E69HN_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F45_E69HN_1200x0.jpg&h=d8bff4d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/77_itEPk_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F77_itEPk_1200x0.jpg&h=a3cda292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/866_sf3Mv_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F866_sf3Mv_1200x0.jpg&h=f7847434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/li_OdxFc_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fli_OdxFc_1200x0.jpg&h=e80da18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/xi_QbMIY_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fxi_QbMIY_1200x0.jpg&h=7c061520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.